### Source Data Requirements

Your web application needs **two data sources**:

| Data Source | Description | Key Columns Used |
|-------------|-------------|------------------|
| **LW_Data** | Last Week's delivery tracking data | Column B: Supplier name, Column J: On-Time/Delay status |
| **CW_Data** | Current Week's delivery tracking data | Column B: Supplier name, Column J: On-Time/Delay status |

**Column J Values:** "On time" or "Delay"

